stylometry: The data mining method we used was desicion trees and clusters. For the cluster I had to cluster data from a bunch of statistics by NFL quarterbacks. I used completions, attempts, yards a game, total yards, touchdowns, and interceptions as my data. I then used the vlookup formula most of the time to gather my cluster into four centers that I had labeled, above average, average, below average, and poor. Once i found the four centers, then i used premium solver and that gave me the most accurate centers and i listed them in the categories.
